Woo proudly presents.... De_tower v16!
This map features:
-Massive destructable towers
-Great fun!
-Long Drops
-High octane action!
-And much more!

Can you travel all the way down the tower, avoiding Ct's firing at you and the long drop? Can you run, avoiding AUG shots and campers, to the bomb site?
Can you plant the bomb then defend it as countless CT's pour in?
No? Then dont be T on this map!

Test your reactions and trigger finger in this fast pased action map!
Deagles only, CT's and T's are pushed to their limits! How would you cope with 16 armed Ct's with deagles, all firing in your direction? Find out!
Dont jump off though, its a long and deadly drop to the bottom!

Check out some more of my maps on our server!
